name: CATDOG
description: CATDOG is a hybrid dog & cat meme coin. The CATDOG game features Mario-style levels where gamers have to collect virtual ICP coins. The virtual ICP is randomly generated at different locations in the game and gives an extra score. Players have to avoid Ethereum ghosts or they lose a life. Upon starting the game, they are given 9 lives, and can get one more by collecting a mushroom. Motoko ghosts are ghosts with superpowers that give users 10 ICP at a time and help them pass the levels faster. The game has 15 levels and the goal is to save CATDOG's girlfriend, Princess Catita, at the final level. The game is complete when Princess Catita is saved at the final level. The supply is capped at 420B tokens and the full supply is trading.
